00:37:47,287 --> 00:37:49,807
Ariel was afraid
you'd feel vandalized.

688
00:37:50,834 --> 00:37:53,352
Ah, don't be silly.
We'll auction off the door.

689
00:37:59,968 --> 00:38:01,828
Mom, you've thanked
your doctors,

690
00:38:01,916 --> 00:38:03,665
